# React

- Functional components only. No `React.FC`. Explicit props interface.
- One component per file. Filename matches export.
- Hooks prefixed `use*`; colocated unless shared.
- No `useEffect` for derived state.
- `React.memo` only with a measured reason.
- Lists: stable keys from domain id.
- Suspense + lazy at route boundaries; Error Boundary above each route.
- Compound components for shared structure.
- No HOCs in new code.
See `.opencode/agents/react.md`.